  "body": "# Problem\n\nThe status client currently has 2 different timestamps for specific messages, in the message overview it displays when a message was received (when I last opened status) whereas in the chat it displays when the message was actually sent.\n\nIt probably makes more sense to display both as when the message was actually sent.\n\n**Overview**\n![IMG_6779](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7621705/56373927-51013100-6202-11e9-89a9-f38a63d96266.jpg)\n\n**Chat**\n![IMG_6780](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7621705/56373933-5494b800-6202-11e9-90f8-150f2da23144.jpg)",
